2026-05-22T05:24:31.4132542Z 21    <!--
2026-05-22T05:24:31.4133160Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-22T05:24:31.4133937Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-22T05:24:31.4175289Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-22T05:24:31.4176668Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-22T05:24:31.4177594Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-22T05:24:31.4179081Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-22T05:24:31.4179978Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-22T05:24:31.4180866Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-22T05:24:31.4181702Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-22T05:24:31.4182526Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-22T05:24:31.4183157Z 32    -->
2026-05-22T05:24:31.4183828Z 33    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
