2026-05-22T05:24:31.5703865Z 271            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-05-22T05:24:31.5704998Z 272            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-22T05:24:31.5705917Z 273            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-22T05:24:31.5706758Z 274            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-22T05:24:31.5707581Z 275            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-22T05:24:31.5708349Z 276            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-22T05:24:31.5709264Z 277            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-22T05:24:31.5710125Z 278            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
